<cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">6 敬佛篇(一三-一四)</cb:mulu><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">3 觀佛部</cb:mulu><cb:mulu level="3" type="其他">感應緣</cb:mulu><cb:mulu level="4" type="其他">唐代州五臺山像變現出聲緣</cb:mulu><cb:div type="other">
